text: Great service. Will definitely  go there to purchase again

Expiry date of promo not clearly indicated. Not a present experience during purchase. Need to do checks on promo before purchase

Bought 1/2 kg of chillie bak kwa. They mixed some with and some without chillie. Regreted that I didn't open my eyes "big big" to watch them packed as I trusted them. The bak kwa is also very dry and not fresh. Will avoid this outlet.

Bought 1 double egg yolk mooncake from this Yee Tee outlet today. Taste soooo awful...... dont know how this stuff can be sold to customers! Totally disappointed. Waste of money! Management should take the quality of their mooncake seriously.
